criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Able to freely give written informed consent to participate in the study and have
             signed the Informed Consent Form;

          2. Males or females, 18> years of age and older inclusive at the time of study
             screening;

          3. American Society of Anesthesiologists (ASA) Class I-III (Appendix III);

          4. Due to undergo ileostomy or colostomy creation via laparotomy or laparoscopy;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Mentally incompetent or unable or unwilling to provide informed consent or comply
             with study procedures;

          2. American Society of Anesthesiologists (ASA) Class IV or V;

          3. Children <18 years
